{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code Chapter 2.36 JUDICIAL REVIEW OF ADMINISTRATIVE 2.36.010 Administrative decisions\u2014Judicial review\u2014Time limits. 2.36.020 Decisions affected.", "num": "2.36", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|2|2.36", "title": "Chapter 2.36 JUDICIAL REVIEW OF ADMINISTRATIVE", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/2.36"}
{"index": {"_id": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/2.36.010", "_type": "page"}}
{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 2.36.010 Administrative decisions\u2014Judicial review\u2014Time limits. The provisions of Section 1094.6 of the Code of Civil Procedure of the state are adopted by the city council, and the provisions are made applicable in the city as further specified in Section 2.36.020 of this chapter. Prior Codifications Previously codified as 2.50.010", "num": "2.36.010", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|2|2.36|2.36.010", "title": "2.36.010 Administrative decisions\u2014Judicial review\u2014Time limits.", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/2.36.010"}
