{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 2.36.020 Decisions affected. The provisions of this chapter shall be applicable to \"decisions,\" as defined by Section 1094.6 of the Code of Civil Procedure of the state, that are final on and after January 1, 1992. Prior Codifications Previously codified as 2.50.020 Cross References Section 2.36.010", "num": "2.36.020", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|2|2.36|2.36.020", "title": "2.36.020 Decisions affected.", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/2.36.020"}
