{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code Chapter 2.58 FILING FEE FOR CANDIDATES 2.58.010 Filing fee. 2.58.020 Waiver.", "num": "2.58", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|2|2.58", "title": "Chapter 2.58 FILING FEE FOR CANDIDATES", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/2.58"}
