{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code Chapter 5.01 SINGLE-USE PLASTIC CARRYOUT BAG REDUCTION 5.01.010 Title. 5.01.020 Purpose and intent. 5.01.030 Definitions. 5.01.040 Single-use plastic carryout bags. 5.01.050 Exemptions. 5.01.060 Enforcement.", "num": "5.01", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|5|5.01", "title": "Chapter 5.01 SINGLE-USE PLASTIC CARRYOUT BAG REDUCTION", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/5.01"}
