dards. 5.06.270 Adult-entertainment businesses providing live entertainment. 5.06.280 Management and security requirements. 5.06.290 Persons under the age of eighteen years prohibited on premises of adult-entertainment business. 5.06.300 Violations. 5.06.310 Regulations nonexclusive. 5.06.320 Applicability to existing adult-entertainment businesses, adult performers and figure models. 5.06.330 Severability.", "num": "5.06", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|5|5.06", "title": "Chapter 5.06 ADULT-ENTERTAINMENT BUSINESSES, ADULT PERFORMERS AND FIGURE MODELS", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/5.06"}
