{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code Chapter 5.10 COMMERCIAL CANNABIS LICENSE 5.10.010 Purpose and intent. 5.10.020 Legal authority. 5.10.030 Cannabis cultivation and commercial cannabis activities prohibited unless specifically authorized by this chapter. 5.10.040 Compliance with state and local laws. 5.10.050 Definitions. 5.10.060 Commercial cannabis business permit required to engage in commercial cannabis business. 5.10.070 Cannabis employee permit required. 5.10.080 Maximum number of authorized commercial cannabis businesses. 5.10.090 Initial application procedure. 5.10.100 Personnel prohibited from holding a license or employee work permit. 5.10.110 Expiration of commercial cannabis business permits. 5.10.120 Revocation of permits. 5.10.130 Renewal applications. 5.10.140 Effect of state license suspension, revocation, or termination. 5.10.150 Appeals. 5.10.160 Written request for appeal. 5.10.170 Appeal hearing. 5.10.180 Permittee selection process. 5.10.190 Change in location\u2014Updated registration form. 5.10.200 Transfer of cannabis business permit. 5.10.210 City business license. 5.10.220 Building permits and inspection. 5.10.230 Certification from the community development director. 5.10.240 Right to occupy and to use property. 5.10.250 Location and design of cannabis businesses. 5.10.260 Limitations on city's liability. 5.10.270 Records and recordkeeping. 5.10.280 Security measures. 5.10.290 Restriction on alcohol and tobacco sales. 5.10.300 Compliance with laws. 5.10.310 Fees and charges. 5.10.320 Miscellaneous operating requirements. 5.10.330 Other operational requirements. 5.10.340 Operating requirements for non-store front retailer. 5.10.350 Non-store front retailer vehicle requirements. 5.10.360 Permissible delivery locations and customers. 5.10.370 Retailer store front services shall not be permitted. 5.10.380 Operating requirements for cultivation facilities. 5.10.390 Operating requirements for testing labs. 5.10.400 Cannabis manufacturing\u2014Edibles and other cannabis products\u2014Sale or distribution of edible and other cannabis products. 5.10.410 Promulgation of regulations, standards and other legal duties. 5.10.420 Community relations. 5.10.430 Fees deemed debt to the city of American Canyon. 5.10.440 Permit holder responsible for violations. 5.10.450 Inspection and enforcement. 5.10.460 Compliance with state regulation. 5.10.470 Violations declared a public nuisance. 5.10.480 Each violation a separate offense. 5.10.490 Criminal penalties. 5.10.500 Remedies cumulative and not exclusive.", "num": "5.10", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|5|5.10", "title": "Chapter 5.10 COMMERCIAL CANNABIS LICENSE", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/5.10"}
