{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 5.20.290 No exclusivity. A franchisee may not require a subscriber or a building owner or manager to enter into an exclusive contract as a condition of providing or continuing service. However, nothing in this chapter prevents a franchisee from entering into an otherwise lawful, mutually desired exclusive arrangement with a building owner or manager of a multiple dwelling unit or commercial subscriber. (Ord. 2005-03, 2005.)", "num": "5.20.290", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|5|5.20|II|5.20.290", "title": "5.20.290 No exclusivity.", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/5.20.290"}
