{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 5.20.320 Additional definitions. \"OVS agreement\" means a contract entered into in accordance with the provisions of this chapter between the city and an OVS franchisee setting forth the terms and conditions under which the franchise will be exercised. (Ord. 2005-03, 2005.)", "num": "5.20.320", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|5|5.20|III|5.20.320", "title": "5.20.320 Additional definitions.", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/5.20.320"}
