{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 5.60.010 Code adoption. The city of American Canyon adopts all those certain documents marked and designated, as Chapter 5.60 to Title 5 of the Napa County Code of Ordinances relating to requirements for elders and or dependent adult caregivers. The documents identified in this section are adopted in their entirety. A copy of the adopted Chapter 5.60 to Title 5 of the Napa County Code of Ordinances relating to requirements for elders and or dependent adult caregivers shall be kept on file in the office of the community development director for use and examination by members of the public. (Ord. 2010-06 \u00a7 1, 2010.) Cross References Section 5.60.020(A)", "num": "5.60.010", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|5|5.60|5.60.010", "title": "5.60.010 Code adoption.", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/5.60.010"}
