{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 8.08.020 Fire chief\u2014Designated. The fire chief of the American Canyon fire protection district is designated as fire chief of the city in order to enforce the Uniform Fire Code within the city limits. (Ord. 93-07 \u00a7 2, 1993.)", "num": "8.08.020", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|8|8.08|8.08.020", "title": "8.08.020 Fire chief\u2014Designated.", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/8.08.020"}
