{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 8.16.111 Severability. This chapter and the various parts thereof are hereby declared to be severable. Should any section of this chapter be declared by the courts to be unconstitutional or invalid, such decision shall not affect the validity of the chapter as a whole, or any portion thereof other than the section so declared to be unconstitutional or invalid.", "num": "8.16.111", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|8|8.16|II|8.16.111", "title": "8.16.111 Severability.", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/8.16.111"}
