{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 8.16.150 Appeals. The city council of the city of American Canyon shall hear and decide appeals when it is alleged there is an error in any requirement, decision or determination made by the floodplain administrator in the enforcement or administration of this chapter . (Ord. 2001-13 \u00a7\u00a7 1, 2, 2001; Ord. 2016-08 \u00a7 1, 2016.)", "num": "8.16.150", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|8|8.16|III|8.16.150", "title": "8.16.150 Appeals.", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/8.16.150"}
