{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 8.18.020 Exemption. The provisions of Section 8.18.010 shall not apply to a duly sworn police officer or deputy sheriff acting in the course of his or her duties. (Ord. 2002-03 \u00a7 1, 2002.)", "num": "8.18.020", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|8|8.18|8.18.020", "title": "8.18.020 Exemption.", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/8.18.020"}
