{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 8.19.020 Violations The violation of this Chapter shall constitute an infraction. This Chapter may be enforced as described in Title 1 of this Code. ( Ord. No. 2023-06 Section 2 .)", "num": "8.19.020", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|8|8.19|8.19.020", "title": "8.19.020 Violations", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/8.19.020"}
