{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 10.44.170 Fines. (A) For each impounding fee for bicycles found to be in violation of the provisions of this chapter , there shall be paid a sum of five dollars. (B) For each violation of the provisions of this article, there shall be a fine of five dollars. (C) After a \"mechanical warning ticket\" is issued advising of the new bike license program, a fine of ten dollars or proof of correction shall be written in. (Ord. 92-19 \u00a7 137, 1992.) Cross References Section 10.48.020", "num": "10.44.170", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|10|10.44|10.44.170", "title": "10.44.170 Fines.", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/10.44.170"}
