{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 10.52.045 Compliance. Notification to Covered Employers. The APCO will provide notice to covered employers within the district regarding the adoption and implementation of this rule by means of written notice and/or email notification. (Ord. 95-12 \u00a7 1, 1995; Ord. 2020-05 \u00a7 5, 2020.)", "num": "10.52.045", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|10|10.52|10.52.045", "title": "10.52.045 Compliance.", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/10.52.045"}
