{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 12.04.090 Playing or practicing golf. No person shall drive, putt or in any other fashion play or practice golf or use golf balls or golf clubs within any city park, playground or other park or playground facility. (Ord. 96-03 \u00a7 9, 1996.)", "num": "12.04.090", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|12|12.04|12.04.090", "title": "12.04.090 Playing or practicing golf.", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/12.04.090"}
