{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 13.04.040 Continuance of district ordinances within city. Each ordinance or enactment of the American Canyon county water district which remains in effect as a city ordinance or enactment by virtue of Section 13.04.010 of this chapter shall be deemed a city ordinance or enactment, and may be modified or superseded by the council in the same manner as other city ordinances or enactments. (Ord. 5 \u00a7 4, 1992.)", "num": "13.04.040", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|13|13.04|13.04.040", "title": "13.04.040 Continuance of district ordinances within city.", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/13.04.040"}
