{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 13.04.050 Enforcement of continuing district ordinances. The enforcement of the district ordinances continuing in effect in the incorporated area shall be by the city. (Ord. 5 \u00a7 5, 1992.)", "num": "13.04.050", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|13|13.04|13.04.050", "title": "13.04.050 Enforcement of continuing district ordinances.", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/13.04.050"}
