{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 14.24.200 Public nuisances. Continued habitation of any building or continued operation of any industrial facility in violation of the provisions of this or any other ordinance, rule or regulation of the city. (Ord. 93-01 \u00a7 513.03.5, 1993; Ord. 98-07 \u00a7 2, 1998.)", "num": "14.24.200", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|14|2|14.24|II|14.24.200", "title": "14.24.200 Public nuisances.", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/14.24.200"}
