{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 14.24.210 Contractor listing. (A) Industrial users which have not achieved consistent compliance with applicable pretreatment standards and requirements are not eligible to receive a contractual award for the sale of goods or services to the city. (B) Existing contracts for the sale of goods or services to the city held by an industrial user found to be in significant violation with pretreatment standards may be terminated at the discretion of the city. (Ord. 93-01 \u00a7 513.03.6, 1993; Ord. 98-07 \u00a7 2, 1998.)", "num": "14.24.210", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|14|2|14.24|II|14.24.210", "title": "14.24.210 Contractor listing.", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/14.24.210"}
