{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 14.24.250 Enforcement response plan. All users are subject to all the provisions of the city enforcement response plan. (Ord. 93-01 \u00a7 513.06, 1993; Ord. 98-07 \u00a7 2, 1998.)", "num": "14.24.250", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|14|2|14.24|III|14.24.250", "title": "14.24.250 Enforcement response plan.", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/14.24.250"}
