{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 14.24.260 Means of enforcement only. The city declares that the foregoing procedures are established as a means of enforcement of the terms and conditions of its ordinances, rules and regulations and not as a penalty. (Ord. 93-01 \u00a7 513.07, 1993; Ord. 98-07 \u00a7 2, 1998.)", "num": "14.24.260", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|14|2|14.24|III|14.24.260", "title": "14.24.260 Means of enforcement only.", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/14.24.260"}
