{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 15.04.060 Anniversary date. Each park owner shall, by May 15, 1994, establish an anniversary date for all rent increases in the park owner's park. Such rent increases, if any, except as specified below, shall be enacted only on the anniversary date of that park. The park owner shall post the anniversary date in the park office or office areas where it can easily be seen by the residents and shall notify the administrator in writing of the anniversary date on or before May 15, 1994. If a park owner wishes to adjust its anniversary date, the park owner may petition the administrator for such change. The administrator shall, in his or her discretion, determine whether the change is acceptable. (Ord. 95-20 \u00a7 1, 1995; Ord. 2011-04 \u00a7 1, 2011.)", "num": "15.04.060", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|15|15.04|15.04.060", "title": "15.04.060 Anniversary date.", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/15.04.060"}
