{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 15.12.110 Disposition of revenues. The fees collected pursuant to this chapter shall be held in separate accounts as deemed appropriate by the city manager and expended solely on the traffic improvements identified in this chapter . (Ord. 99-18 \u00a7 1, 1999; Ord. 2015-02 \u00a7 9, 2015.)", "num": "15.12.110", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|15|15.12|15.12.110", "title": "15.12.110 Disposition of revenues.", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/15.12.110"}
