{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 16.01.020 Purpose. Building Codes are adopted as a means of regulating the construction, alteration, and maintenance of buildings. This Building and Construction Code is intended to: (A) Promote the health, safety, and welfare of the residents of the city of American Canyon and other persons visiting the city; and (B) Ensure compliance with local, state, and nationally adopted standards and methods of building construction; and (C) Enable the building official to enforce the provisions of this title . (Ord. 2013-06 \u00a7 3, 2013; Ord. 2019-11 \u00a7 3, 2019; Ord. 2022-05 \u00a7 2, 2022.)", "num": "16.01.020", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|16|16.01|16.01.020", "title": "16.01.020 Purpose.", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/16.01.020"}
