{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 16.12.010 Intent. This chapter establishes standard placards to be used to indicate the condition of a structure for continued occupancy. The chapter further authorizes the building official and his or her authorized representatives to post the appropriate placard at each entry point to a building or structure upon completion of a safety assessment.", "num": "16.12.010", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|16|16.12|16.12.010", "title": "16.12.010 Intent.", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/16.12.010"}
