{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 16.12.020 Application of provisions. The provisions of this chapter are applicable to all buildings and structures of all occupancies regulated by the city of American Canyon. The council may extend the provisions as necessary. (Ord. 2008-12, 2008.)", "num": "16.12.020", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|16|16.12|16.12.020", "title": "16.12.020 Application of provisions.", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/16.12.020"}
