{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 16.12.030 Definitions. \"Safety assessment\" means a visual, nondestructive examination of a building or structure for the purpose of determining the condition for continued occupancy. (Ord. 2008-12, 2008.)", "num": "16.12.030", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|16|16.12|16.12.030", "title": "16.12.030 Definitions.", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/16.12.030"}
