{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 16.14.020 Applicability. (A) Applicability. Final landscape plans shall be required for the following landscape projects: (1) New construction and rehabilitated landscapes for public agency projects, private development projects and developer-installed single-family and multifamily projects, requiring a building permit, plan check or design permit; (2) Cemeteries. Recognizing the special landscape management needs of cemeteries, new and rehabilitated cemeteries are limited to Sections 16.14.070 , 16.14.140 and 16.14.160 ; and existing cemeteries are limited to Sections 16.14.160 and 16.14.170 . (B) This chapter does not apply to: (1) Registered local, state or federal historical sites; (2) Ecological restoration projects that do not require a permanent irrigation system; (3) Plant collections, as part of botanical gardens and arboretums open to the public. (Ord. 2015-05 \u00a7 2, 2015.) Cross References Section 16.14.040 Section 16.14.160(B)", "num": "16.14.020", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|16|16.14|16.14.020", "title": "16.14.020 Applicability.", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/16.14.020"}
