{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 19.04.010 Purpose. The purpose of this chapter is to define terms used in this title and establish rules for the construction of the language to ensure a consistent interpretation of the requirements of this title . (Ord. 2001-02 \u00a7 1, 2001.)", "num": "19.04.010", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|19|1|19.04|19.04.010", "title": "19.04.010 Purpose.", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/19.04.010"}
