{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 19.05.010 Purpose. The purpose of these provisions is to classify uses according to types on the basis of common functional, product, or compatibility characteristics, and to set forth permitted and conditionally-permitted uses for each zoning district. Notwithstanding any provision in this code to the contrary, any use of land, operation, or business that is in violation of state and/or federal law shall be prohibited in all specific plan areas, districts, and/or zones within the city. (Ord. 2001-02 \u00a7 1, 2001; Ord. 2009-08 \u00a7 2, 2009.)", "num": "19.05.010", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|19|1|19.05|19.05.010", "title": "19.05.010 Purpose.", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/19.05.010"}
