ict \"REC\" denotes Recreation District (Ord. 2001-02 \u00a7 1, 2001; Ord. 2009-15 \u00a7 3, 2009; Ord. 2010-03 \u00a7 3, 2010; Ord. 2010-05 \u00a7 1, 2010; Ord. 2018-01 \u00a7 1, 2018; Ord. 2018-05 \u00a7 6, 2018.) Cross References Section 19.15.030(2)", "num": "19.15.020", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|19|2|19.15|19.15.020", "title": "19.15.020 Permitted uses.", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/19.15.020"}
