{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 19.20.010 Purpose. The purpose of the Paoli Light Industrial Commercial Overlay District is to accommodate commercial and commercially related uses that capitalize on vehicle access and visibility from Highway 29 and Newell Drive and serve industrial uses in the City's Industrial Parks. ( Ord. No. 2024-01 .)", "num": "19.20.010", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|19|2|19.20|19.20.010", "title": "19.20.010 Purpose.", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/19.20.010"}
{"index": {"_id": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/19.20.020", "_type": "page"}}
{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 19.20.020 Allowable uses. (A) Property in the Paoli Light Industrial Commercial Overlay District may be used either for industrial purposes, consistent with the permitted and conditionally permitted uses allowed by this title for the underlying Paoli Light Industrial (PLI) base zone district, or for commercial purposes 1 . (B) The following uses as defined in use classifications, are permitted 1 : (1) Public and quasi-public uses: (a) Charitable uses (b) Public information center (c) Utilities, minor (2) Commercial uses: (a) Ambulance Services (b) Bank, savings and loan, including walk-up service (c) Bookstore (d) Catering (e) Drugstore (f) Food Sales (g) Lodging services (h) Maintenance and Repair Services (i) Personal services (j) Restaurant (k) Restaurant, Night Use (l) Restaurant, take-out (m) Retail sales (n) Zero Emission Vehicle Service Station (C) The following uses as defined in use classifications, are permitted subject to a conditional use permit 1 : (1) Commercial uses: (a) Automobile rental (b) Entertainment, indoor (c) On-premises liquor consumption, tasting room (d) Personal Improvement Services (e) Vehicle/equipment sales and service ( Ord. No. 2024-01 .)", "num": "19.20.020", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|19|2|19.20|19.20.020", "title": "19.20.020 Allowable uses.", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/19.20.020"}
