{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 19.22.080 Stormwater management. All landscape plans shall conform to Chapter 14.28 Stormwater and Pollution Discharge Control Program. (Ord. 2015-05 \u00a7 3, 2015.)", "num": "19.22.080", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|19|2|19.22|19.22.080", "title": "19.22.080 Stormwater management.", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/19.22.080"}
