{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 19.23.020 Applicability. A sign may be constructed, erected, placed, established, painted, created or maintained in the city only in conformance with the standards, procedures, exemptions and other requirements of this chapter . (Ord. 2011-03 \u00a7 2, 2011.)", "num": "19.23.020", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|19|2|19.23|19.23.020", "title": "19.23.020 Applicability.", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/19.23.020"}
