{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 19.24.010 Purpose. The purpose of these provisions is to protect, preserve and enhance the significant biological habitats, plants and wildlife within the city, consistent with the American Canyon general plan. (Ord. 2001-02 \u00a7 1, 2001.)", "num": "19.24.010", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|19|2|19.24|19.24.010", "title": "19.24.010 Purpose.", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/19.24.010"}
