{"body": "City of American Canyon Municipal Code 19.39.080 Operational standards (A) The accessory dwelling unit may not be sold separately from the primary residence. (B) Owner-Occupancy. The property owner shall reside in either the primary residence or the accessory dwelling unit except accessory dwelling unit and junior accessory dwelling unit applications submitted between January 1, 2020 to January 1, 2025. (C) An accessory dwelling unit may not be rented for transient occupancy (less than thirty consecutive days). ( Ord. No. 2024-04 Section 6 ; Ord. 2017-05 \u00a7 2, 2017; Ord. 2020-04 \u00a7 1, 2020.)", "num": "19.39.080", "path": "library|City of American Canyon, Cal., Code|19|2|19.39|19.39.080", "title": "19.39.080 Operational standards", "url": "/us/ca/cities/american-canyon/code/19.39.080"}
